Quickstrike:




It began to rain at the freshness of the night. It could be hear from 
the rythmeous banging against the metal of the base. Looking past 
Quasar, Quickstrike stood up. He hear voices down the cooridor that 
sounded urgent to his audios. He stepped towards the frame of the 
doorway, listening in. He could feel the offspring eyeing him.

"Ah think there's somethin' goin' on," he said to the two 
females. "Ah'm gonna go check it out. Be right back." He walked out, 
a little relieved to get away, but still wanting to go back to Black 
Arachnia.
